    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced leek </strong>and<strong> diced carrot</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1648553935849-x200.jpg",
